snippet.title: ART for Snakes release trailer (free game)
snippet.description:
Eat your way through over 10 delicious courses of the finest paintings in ART for Snakes, a free snakeformer by Splerp, Cheeseness, and lcl.

Available for Linux and Windows at https://splerp.itch.io/art-for-snakes
